HSBC Advisor Funds Trust - HSBC Investor International Equity Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 12:00 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of HSBC Advisor Funds Trust - HSBC Investor International Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of December 31, 2011 HSBC Advisor Funds Trust - HSBC Investor International Equity Fund has gone out of business. HSBC Advisor Funds Trust - HSBC Investor International Equity Fund is an open-ended feeder fund launched and managed by HSBC Global Asset Management (USA) Inc. The fund invests its corpus in the HSBC Investor Funds - HSBC Investor International Equity Portfolio. HSBC Advisor Funds Trust - HSBC Investor International Equity Fund was formed on January 9, 1995 and is domiciled in the United States.


452 Fifth Avenue7th FloorNew York, NY 10018United StatesFounded in 1995



Phone: 212-525-5000

Fax: 212-525-2322








Key Executives for HSBC Advisor Funds Trust - HSBC Investor International Equity Fund


HSBC Advisor Funds Trust - HSBC Investor International Equity Fund does not have any Key Executives recorded. 





